m 66 (2009): 1438-67[5] "Product Information. VFEND (voriconazole)." Pfizer U.S. Pharmaceuticals, New York, NY.[6] "Product Information. Torisel (temsirolimus)." Wyeth-Ayerst Laboratories, Philadelphia, PA.', 'Anidulafungin, Micafungin, Caspofungin, Oteseconazole', 'Trametinib, Afatinib, Dacomitinib, Tivozanib, Alectinib', 1767369485);
